{"comments":"TypeStyle - a complete typographic specification.\n\nA molecule combining typography atoms into a usable style:\n- FontFamily (or FontStack for fallbacks)\n- FontWeight\n- FontSize\n- LineHeight\n- LetterSpacing\n- TextTransform\n\nTypeStyles are the building blocks of a TypeHierarchy. Each semantic\nlevel (H1, H2, body, etc.) maps to a TypeStyle.\n\nExample from Sentience brand guide:\n- HL-H3: Archivo ExtraBold, UPPERCASE, tracking 25, line-height 1.3\n- Body: Poppins Regular, Normal case, tracking 40, line-height 1.6\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Typography","TypeStyle"],"TypeStyle"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[123,44],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Typography/TypeStyle.purs","start":[123,1]},"title":"eqTypeStyle"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Typography","TypeStyle"],"TypeStyle"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[133,12],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Typography/TypeStyle.purs","start":[125,1]},"title":"showTypeStyle"}],"comments":"Complete typographic style specification\n\nCombines all typography atoms into a cohesive style that can be\napplied to text elements.\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"newtype","declType":"data","roles":[],"typeArguments":[]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[121,4],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Typography/TypeStyle.purs","start":[114,1]},"title":"TypeStyle"},{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Dat